Wasit Governorate (Carabi: Ciraaq, Turjubaan Wāsit) waa guddoomiye ku yaal bariga Ciraaq, koonfur bari ee Ciraaq iyo xuduudaha Iran. Ka hor 1976 waxaa loo yaqaan gobolka Kut. Magaalooyinka waaweyn waxaa ka mid ah caasimada Al Kut, Al-Hai iyo Al-Suwaira. Guddoomiyuhu wuxuu ka kooban yahay Mesobotamian Marshes of Shuwayja, Al-Attariyah, iyo Hor Aldelmj. Magaciisa wuxuu ka yimid erey carabi ah oo macneheedu yahay "dhexda", sida magaalada hore ee Wasit jiifsatay Tigris ku saabsan bartamaha dhexe ee u dhaxeeya Baghdad iyo Basra. Magaalada mayit ka baxday kaddib markii ay kor u dhaaftay Tigris.
